		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><a name="3590"></a><span class="name"><span class="usercolor">Koori</span></span><div class="gensmall"><img src="images/ranks/rank_1.gif" alt="Enchanter" title="Enchanter" border="0" /><br />Enchanter</div><div align="center"><img src="http://www.geocities.com/jeremy_moffitt/images/everquest/lilwhale.gif" alt="Avatar" border="0" /></div><br /><div align="left" class="gensmall">Gender:&nbsp;Unknown</div></td>
                <td class="row1" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                        <tr>
                                <td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=3590&amp;sid=14d6c7cf1160dbc8603d1f35971a8a6f#3590"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Sun Aug 17, 2003 12:15 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Quest To Be A Froggy (Long)</span></td>
                                <td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=3590&amp;sid=14d6c7cf1160dbc8603d1f35971a8a6f"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>    </td>
